        <h1>Common CCR009 Reporting Mistakes Motor Dealers Should Avoid</h1>
        <p class="ccr009-hero__lead">CCR009 is an important FCA regulatory return for many FCA-authorised motor dealers. While the return is generally straightforward, reporting problems often occur because information is incomplete, records are disorganised or preparation begins too late.</p>
        <p class="ccr009-hero__lead">Understanding the most common CCR009 reporting mistakes can help motor dealers prepare more effectively, reduce unnecessary administration and improve the accuracy of information submitted through the FCA's RegData system.</p>
